title: Coach's Owner Tapestry Files Trademark Infringement Suit Against Shein
body: Like its chief fast-fashion rival Temu, Shein is facing multiple cases of trademark infringement by companies and artists.

title: Forever 21 says 'de minimis' exemption used by Shein and Temu is partly responsible for its second bankruptcy
body: Forever 21 said it can't compete with e-commerce companies that send small packages without paying tariffs via the "de minimis" exemption.
